                <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.J.14.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 68, 4b</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian"
                        notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00"
                        >undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>Add the following Article to the Peace Treaty (Part VII of the Draft): <quote
                        rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“Italy undertakes to pay compensation for the loss and damage sustained
                            by Greek nationals as the result of illegal actions committed by Italy
                            or Italian authorities subsequent to 1/9/1939 and before Greece came
                            into the war. The claims will be lodged with the Conciliation Commission
                            provided for in Article 72 of the draft Peace Treaty with Italy.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
